{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1d66d6acb0","title":"中央文革小组关于斗争潘梓年的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4fe97e7c34","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":9,"articleId":"1d66d6acb0","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"清查五·一六","id":"a0d5508956","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"87dfa5c6ff","name":"中央文革"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d35bb7c228","type":"title","text":"中央文革小组关于斗争潘梓年的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5fd1367bb","type":"paragraph","text":"斗潘梓年，你们联合起来斗，你们要商量好，把准备工作作好，定好时间，再来电话请示，把人带去。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f5cc4278f6","type":"paragraph","text":"领导上说了，你们联合起来斗，大批判应当联合起来搞，不能单方面去斗。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7872be31c","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组李春俊传达 67.10.9  18：55","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"708b10062f","type":"paragraph","text":"十月十日上午10：00又来电话：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41b1bdbaac","type":"paragraph","text":"要联合起来斗，这是中央首长指示精神，不是我们随便说的。你们可以将这个精神告诉大批判指挥部一下，也可以向群众传达一下。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e40032d982","type":"paragraph","text":"李春俊","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1d66d6acb0","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}